Mage's Association, Celestine Baudelaire,

10
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:19,860
and I personally received it from her.

11
00:02:19,860 --> 00:02:21,400
From Celes?

12
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:24,250
Not to mention the reward's 
high for how simple it is.

13
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:27,120
So it includes reparations 
for the incident with Galluk?

14
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,790
Well, I imagine that's true.

15
00:02:29,790 --> 00:02:31,250
I won't be going.

16
00:02:31,250 --> 00:02:31,980
Huh?

17
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:34,750
I don't want to owe Celes any favors.

18
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:36,960
I wouldn't mind if it were a normal mission,

19
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:40,060
but I'm not taking on a quest from her 
with an unnecessarily high reward.

20
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:42,260
<i>She's strict on herself.</i>

21
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:44,520
But honestly, this is a boon for us.

22
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:47,070
We don't have that much money.

23
00:02:47,770 --> 00:02:49,680
It's a simple mission,

24
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:52,570
so I think you'll be fine even 
if you're not all together.

25
00:02:52,570 --> 00:02:54,920
What do you say, Diablo?

26
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,280
<i>I guess I could split the reward</i>

27
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,060
<i>we earn from this mission by 
paying Rem my lodging fee.</i>

28
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:08,280
If you don't want to come,
then stay here in the city by yourself.

29
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,410
I will.

30
00:03:09,410 --> 00:03:10,510
Great!

31
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:12,920
So you and Shera-chan will be going, then?

32
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:14,670
That settles it.

33
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:15,930
I'm counting on you!

34
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:20,300
Go to the Bridge of Ulug 
and deliver refreshments...

35
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,610
So easy!

36
00:03:21,610 --> 00:03:23,430
This really is a reparation...

37
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:26,590
Does Celes really think I'd accept this

38
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:30,310
