and deliver a slashing blow.</i>

119
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:39,400
<i>It's a standard opening move.</i>

120
00:05:40,610 --> 00:05:41,520
<i>Huh?</i>

121
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:45,030
<i>Am I actually getting excited 
for the first time in a while?</i>

122
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,710
<i>A standard opening move like Sword Smite</i>

123
00:05:47,710 --> 00:05:50,480
<i>is doomed to be seen through in PVP.</i>

124
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:56,220
<i>Skilled players will use the rushing 
motion of Sword Smite, cancel the slash,</i>

125
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:58,790
<i>and chain it to their next attack.</i>

126
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:03,050
Heh Heh Heh...

127
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:02,600
Isn't Diablo acting a little weird?

128
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:04,090
